org.alljoyn.bus.ifaces
Interface AllSeenIntrospectable

@BusInterface(name="org.allseen.Introspectable")
public interface AllSeenIntrospectable

The org.allseen.Introspectable interface provides introspection xml that contains description elements that document the object and it's various sub-elements.

Method Summary
